passages.name: name
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[errorCoInsured]]"
          when="coInsured > 6"
>
</Redirect>

<Message>
  What’s your name?
</Message>

<TextActionSet next="[[Continue->birthDate]]">
  <TextAction title="First name"
              placeholder="Hedvig"
              large="true"
              key="firstName"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="Surname"
              placeholder="Hedvigsen"
              large="true"
              key="lastName"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: size
passages.text:
<Message>
  Okay. How many square meters is it?
</Message>

<Response>
  {livingSpace} square meters
</Response>

<NumberAction placeholder="52"
              key="livingSpace"
              minvalue="1"
              next="[[Continue->address]]"
              unit="square meters"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      Size
    </Title>
    <Description>
      The size of your home and the area we’ll insure. The exact square meters can often be found in your lease or in your contract of sale.
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</NumberAction>

passages.name: NewsletterSuccess
passages.text: Double-click this passage to edit it.

passages.name: studentEligibilityCheck
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[Offer]]"
          when="birthDate.Age > 30 || livingSpace > 50 || coInsured > 0"
          key="isStudent"
          value="false"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[student]]"
          when="true"
>
</Redirect>

passages.name: errorSize
passages.text:
<Message>
  We’re sorry, currently our insurance only cover homes up to 250 square meters
</Message>

<Message>
  Please subscribe to our newsletter and be the first to know when we are able to insure larger homes
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option>
    [[Sign up for our newsletter->NewsletterSuccess]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: email
passages.text:
<Message>
  Lastly, your email address?
</Message>

<TextAction placeholder="email@address.com"
            mask="Email"
            key="email"
            next="[[Continue->studentEligibilityCheck]]"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      Email
    </Title>
    <Description>
      Your email address will only be used to provide you with a price offer.
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</TextAction>

passages.name: offerSuccess
passages.text: Double-click this passage to edit it.

passages.name: coInsured
passages.text:
<Message>
  Great. How many people will the insurance cover?
</Message>

<Response>
  <when expression="coInsured == 1">
    We're 2
  </when>
  <when expression="coInsured > 1">
    We're {coInsured+1}
  </when>
  <when expression="coInsured == 0">
    Just me
  </when>
</Response>

<NumberAction placeholder="2"
              key="coInsured"
              minvalue="1"
              next="[[Continue->name]]"
              unit="people (incl.myself)"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      Insured People
    </Title>
    <Description>
      You and the people you live with. It could be your partner, kids, roommates. All whom can be covered by the insurance.
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</NumberAction>

passages.name: offerError
passages.text:
<Message>
  Sorry, something went wrong. We’re unable to give you a price quote right now. Try again, if it doesn’t work please write us in the chat on the website. Thank you!
</Message>

passages.name: offerUwLimit
passages.text:
<Message>
  Unfortunately, we’re unable to give you an offer via our website. Please email us att prisforslag@hedvig.com and one of our insurance experts will look over your application. Thank you!
</Message>

passages.name: student
passages.text:
<Message>
  Are you perhaps a student? If so, our student offer is something for you.
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="isStudent"
          value="true"
  >
    [[Yes I’m a student->Offer]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="isYouth"
          value="false"
  >
    [[No, not a student->Offer]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: birthDate
passages.text:
<Message>
  And your date of birth?
</Message>

<Response>
  {birthDate}
</Response>

<TextAction placeholder="yyyy-mm-dd"
            key="birthDate"
            minvalue="1"
            mask="BirthDate"
            next="[[Continue->email]]"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      Date of birth
    </Title>
    <Description>
      To give you an exact price we need to know your age. We’ll not use your birthdate for anything else.
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</TextAction>

passages.name: address
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[errorSize]]"
          when="size > 250"
>
</Redirect>

<Message>
  What’s your address?
</Message>

<Response>
  {street}, {zipCode}
</Response>

<TextActionSet next="[[Continue->coInsured]]">
  <TextAction title="Address"
              placeholder="Examplestreet 21"
              large="true"
              key="street"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="Postal code"
              mask="NorwegianPostalCode"
              placeholder="0123"
              key="zipCode"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: errorCoInsured
passages.text:
<Message>
  We’re sorry, currently our insurance only cover homes with a maximum of 6 people
</Message>

<Message>
  Please subscribe to our newsletter and be the first to know when we are able to insure homes your size
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option>
    [[Sign up for our newsletter->NewsletterSuccess]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>
